Patch Set 7:

This could benefit from converting:

 ostid_to_fid(&info->fti_fid, &oi, ofd->ofd_lut.lut_lsd.lsd_osd_index);

to calls to a new function:

 int tgt_ostid_to_fid(struct lu_target *tgt, struct lu_fid *fid, struct ost_id *ostid);

or 

 int ofd_ostid_to_fid(struct ofd_device *ofd, struct lu_fid *fid, struct ost_id *ostid);

It would also be a good time to fix ostid_to_fid() so that the ostid parameter is const qualified. Then the ostid parameter of the two functions above should be const as well.
